Pulse is normal, too.

00:00:18.018 --> 00:00:19.644 position:50% align:center
Then, don't tell me...

00:00:19.728 --> 00:00:21.771 position:50% align:center
Did your company tank?

00:00:21.855 --> 00:00:22.731 position:50% align:center
No.

00:00:22.814 --> 00:00:24.315 position:50% align:center
Did you kill somebody?

00:00:24.399 --> 00:00:25.650 position:50% align:center
I did not.

00:00:25.734 --> 00:00:28.278 position:50% align:center
